  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a artificer, you gain the following class features.</p>\n<h5>Hit Points</h5>\n<p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d8 per artificer level</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 18 + your Constitution modifier</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d8 (or 5) + your Constitution modifier per artificer level after 1st</p>\n<h5>Proficiencies</h5>\n<p><strong>Armor:</strong> Light armor, medium armor</p>\n<p><strong>Weapons:</strong> Simple weapons</p>\n<p><strong>Tools:</strong> Artificer's tools, tinker's tools, and one other type of tools of your choice</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Constitution, Intelligence</p>\n<p><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose two from Arcana, History, Investigation, Medicine, Nature, Perception, Sleight of Hand</p>\n<h5>Equipment</h5>\n<p>You start one of the following equipment options, in addition to the equipment granted by your background:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>An arcane focus, a spellbook, a dagger, a light crossbow with 20 bolts, a lorekeeper's pack, and 20 gp</li>\n<li>100 gp worth of equipment, and an equipment pack</li>\n</ul>",
